    "asOf": "2021-01-25",
    "date": "2021-05-05T14:35:57Z",
    "text": "Building United States Infrastructure and Leveraging Development Act or the BUILD Act\n\nThis bill increases from $15 billion to $30 billion the national limitation on the amount of tax-exempt highway or surface freight transfer facility bonds.\n\nThe bill also applies the prevailing wage requirements of the Davis-Bacon Act to projects funded by bond issues."
